Package com.cafean.client.values.util.matlab

Interface EngineLibrary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.Library
    public interface EngineLibrary
extends com.sun.jna.Library
    MATLAB Engine Library.

    Calls to the engine library should always be made from the same thread.
